{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ScrollTimeline","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScrollTimeline","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","browserCompat":["api.ScrollTimeline"],"sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></strong></li><li><strong><em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScrollTimeline\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>ScrollTimeline</code></a></em></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScrollTimeline/ScrollTimeline\"><code>ScrollTimeline()</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScrollTimeline/axis\"><code>axis</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScrollTimeline/source\"><code>source</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Web Animations</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationPlaybackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/getAnimations\"><code>Element.getAnimations()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ViewTimeline\"><code>ViewTimeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","sidebarMacro":"APIRef","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>ScrollTimeline</code></strong> interface of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\" title=\"Web Animations API\">Web Animations API</a> represents a scroll progress timeline (see <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_scroll-driven_animations\">CSS scroll-driven animations</a> for more details).</p>\n<p>Pass a <code>ScrollTimeline</code> instance to the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\" title=\"Animation()\"><code>Animation()</code></a> constructor or the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\" title=\"animate()\"><code>animate()</code></a> method to specify it as the timeline that will control the progress of the animation.</p><svg viewBox=\"-1 -1 650 42\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"136\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"68\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      AnimationTimeline\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"136\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"166\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"136,14 146,9 146,19 136,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScrollTimeline\" aria-current=\"page\">\n    <rect x=\"166\" y=\"0\" width=\"112\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#F4F7F8\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"222\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      ScrollTimeline\n    </text>\n  </a></svg>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructor","title":"Constructor","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"scrolltimeline\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScrollTimeline/ScrollTimeline\" title=\"ScrollTimeline()\"><code>ScrollTimeline()</code></a> <abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Creates a new <code>ScrollTimeline</code> object instance.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instance_properties","title":"Instance properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>This interface also inherits the properties of its parent, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code></a>.</em></p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"source\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScrollTimeline/source\" title=\"source\"><code>source</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span> <abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns a reference to the scrollable element (<em>scroller</em>) whose scroll position is driving the progress of the timeline and therefore the animation.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"axis\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScrollTimeline/axis\" title=\"axis\"><code>axis</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span> <abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns an enumerated value representing the scroll axis that is driving the progress of the timeline.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instance_methods","title":"Instance methods","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>This interface inherits the methods of its parent, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code></a>.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"displaying_the_source_and_axis_of_a_scroll_progress_timeline","title":"Displaying the source and axis of a scroll progress timeline","isH3":true,"content":"<p>In this example, we animate an element with a <code>class</code> of <code>box</code> along a view progress timeline â€” it animates across the screen as the document scrolls. We output the <code>source</code> element and scroll <code>axis</code> to an <code>output</code> element in the top-right corner.</p>\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n<p>The HTML for the example is shown below.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">html</span></p><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>content<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>box<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>output<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"css\">CSS</h4>\n<p>The CSS for the example looks like this:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">css</span></p><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.content</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2000px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> rebeccapurple<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fixed<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.output</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Arial<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Helvetica<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fixed<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h4>\n<p>In the JavaScript, we grab references to the <code>box</code> and <code>output</code> <code>&lt;div&gt;</code>s, then create a new <code>ScrollTimeline</code>, specifying that the element that will drive the scroll timeline progress is the document (<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/html\"><code>&lt;html&gt;</code></a>) element, and the scroll axis is the <code>block</code> axis. We then animate the <code>box</code> element with the Web Animations API. Last of all, we display the source element and axis in the <code>output</code> element.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> box <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\".box\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> output <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\".output\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> timeline <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ScrollTimeline</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">source</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>documentElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">axis</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"block\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">animate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">rotate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"0deg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"720deg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">left</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"0%\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"100%\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    timeline<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\noutput<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Timeline source element: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>timeline<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>source<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeName<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">. Timeline scroll axis: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>timeline<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>axis<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"result\">Result</h4>\n<p>Scroll to see the box being animated.</p><div class=\"code-example\" id=\"sect2\"><p class=\"example-header\"></p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Displaying the source and axis of a scroll progress timeline sample\" id=\"frame_displaying_the_source_and_axis_of_a_scroll_progress_timeline\" width=\"100%\" height=\"320px\" src=\"http://localhost:5042/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScrollTimeline/runner.html?id=displaying_the_source_and_axis_of_a_scroll_progress_timeline\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/scroll-animations/#scrolltimeline-interface","title":"Scroll-driven Animations"}],"query":"api.ScrollTimeline"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.ScrollTimeline"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_scroll-driven_animations\">CSS scroll-driven animations</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ViewTimeline\"><code>ViewTimeline</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Constructor","id":"constructor"},{"text":"Instance properties","id":"instance_properties"},{"text":"Instance methods","id":"instance_methods"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The ScrollTimeline interface of the Web Animations API represents a scroll progress timeline (see CSS scroll-driven animations for more details).","popularity":0.0032,"modified":"2023-07-07T07:19:19.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/scrolltimeline","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/api/scrolltimeline/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/acfe8c9f1f4145f77653a2bc64a9744b001358dc","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"ScrollTimeline","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScrollTimeline","title":"ScrollTimeline"}],"pageTitle":"ScrollTimeline - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}